name: Tripwalker T-006
description: The sixth Tripwalker animated avatar ever minted on the Tezos blockchain, available for the first time for sale on HEN. Each Tripwalker is uniquely minted, 1/1, and no two Tripwalkers ever share the same combination of traits. Only 100 Tripwalker avatars will ever be created, starting with T-001 and ending with T-100.
